name: MigraineICD9
title: Migraine (ICD9)
description: This value set includes ICD9CM concepts for migraine headache.
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This value set includes ICD9CM concepts for migraine headache.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify people diagnosed with migraine headache. This element may map to "Diagnosis" Category of the Quality Data Model.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes concepts for migraine headache (pain in head).),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes concepts for cyclical vomiting, ophthalmoplegic migraine, and abdominal migraine.)
